quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  2,49,"Onon ɓiɓɓe Isra'il ciftoree nde Min ndanndi on e boneeji yimɓe Fir'awna, ɓe pawii on kala lette, nde ɓe kirsi sukaaɓe mon worɓe haa mbaason heddaade, ɓe ngacca sukaaɓe mon rewɓe ngam ɓe ngollana ɓe, ɓe koyni on, ko jooma mon danndi on boneeji fir'awna e wallidiiɓe mum ngam humpitaade on, mbela joo njetton Mbo."
  2,50,"Ciftoree moƴƴere nde Min mbaɗani on, Min peccani on maayo ngo woni laawol njoorndi ndew-ɗon heen, Min ndanndi on, Min njooli fir'awna e wondiiɓe mum yeeso mon, oɗon ndaarda ɓe gite mon ŋaas."
  2,51,"Ciftoree e ɗiin moƴƴi ko Min podondirnoo e Muusaa jammaaji capanɗe nayi ngam jippinde heen Tawreeta wona fooyre (yaynannde) e peewal, alaa ko mbaɗɗon heen sonaa oɗon ndewa ngaari, baɗal mon ngal ko tooñe mawɗe."
  2,52,"Rewi heen Min ngaccani on ɓaawo nde tuub-ɗon, Min leɓtaani on mbela joo njettiron Alla rewde Mo e ɗoftaade Mo no haaniri."
  2,53,"Ciftoree e ɗii moƴƴi, nde Min ndokki Muusaa (jkm)deftere (Tawreeta) seerndoore hakkunde goonga e fenaande,e hakkunde peewal e majjere haa njiiton goonga jokkon mbo."
  2,54,"Ciftoree e ɗiin moƴƴi, nde Alla ñaawani on accude rewde ngaari ndi, nde Muusaa (jkm) wii on: on tooñii ko'e mon e rewde mon ngaari ndi, tuubee ndutto-ɗon e tagɗo on O, mbarondiron, ɗuum ɓuri e mon jokkude keefeeru caasnoowu jayngol, on mbaɗii ɗuum e ballal Alla, O accani on, sabu ko keewɗo yaafaade jurmotooɗo jeyaaɓe Makko."
  2,55,"Ciftoree nde baabiraaɓe mon ɓee kaaldi e Muusaa e cuusal, ɓe mbii: min ngoonɗintaa ma haa min jiira Alla gite amen ko laaɓi,ndeen jayngol cumowol ɓami on,ngol wari on oɗon ndaarondira."
  2,56,"Rewti heen Min immintini on ɓaawo maayde mon mbela njetton Alla sabu ko O moƴƴi e mon."
  2,57,"Na jeyaa e moƴƴi Amen dow mon, Min neldi duule ɗuwo-ɗon heen nguli naange nde majju-ɗon nde, Min njippini dow mon njuumri welndi, e colli juɗaaɗi, Min mbii on: ñaamee moƴƴi ɗi Min njeɗe on. Yeddugol maɓɓe alaa ko ustataa Min, kono ko ko'e maɓɓe ɓe tooñi, ɓe ustoraa baraaji lette ngoodana ɓe."